05:56.681 --> 05:59.666
And then he says, I thank thee to

06:00.066 --> 06:15.000
that all my joy is touched with pain, that shadows fall on brightest hours and thorns remain, so that earth's bliss may be my guide and not my chain.

06:16.622 --> 06:23.148
