08:39.938 --> 08:45.686
sufficient in Pauline terms for a completely free approach to life.

08:47.328 --> 08:50.853
Absolutely free in need of nothing else according to Paul.

08:51.534 --> 08:52.014
What was it?

08:52.896 --> 08:59.204
