09:23.195 --> 09:24.697
All God's children got shoes.

09:25.257 --> 09:30.522
When I get to heaven, going to put on my shoes, I'm going to walk all over God's heaven.

09:32.705 --> 09:38.290
Because that which was there far outweighed the this, which was now.

09:38.818 --> 09:47.009
And it is a problem for Western Christianity when the now so far outweighs any prospect of the then.

09:47.610 --> 09:49.293
