11:26.242 --> 11:39.621
No matter how good they look on Sunday morning, I know this, that the vast majority of their lives, at some point along the way, are marked by quiet desperation.

11:40.542 --> 11:45.028
And I know that pesterly, because I know the challenge in my own heart.

11:45.048 --> 11:47.291
