48:52.251 --> 48:57.077
Lay down, O weary one, lay down, your head upon my breast.

48:58.198 --> 49:01.962
I came to Jesus as I was weary, worn, and sad.

49:02.683 --> 49:06.688
I found in him a resting place, and he has made me glad.

49:07.589 --> 49:12.274
I heard the voice of Jesus say, I am this dark world's light.

49:12.930 --> 49:17.134
Look unto me your mournful rise and all your days be bright.

49:18.295 --> 49:24.541
I came to Jesus as I was and found in him my light my son.

49:25.462 --> 49:30.287
And in that light of life I walk till the traveling days are done.

49:30.327 --> 49:33.350
That love once is the testimony of the Christian.

49:34.070 --> 49:41.938
It may well be that you are sitting here right now and you have never moved from

49:42.594 --> 49:49.164
and assent to the things that you are credibly prepared to say about Jesus.

49:50.346 --> 49:53.431
And yet you have never committed your life to Him.

49:53.451 --> 49:55.575
You've never actually come to Him.

49:56.336 --> 49:58.640
You've never actually bowed your knee to Him.

49:59.461 --> 50:02.706
And loved ones, that is the greatest need of the entire world.

50:03.447 --> 50:05.350
And that is all of our greatest needs.

50:06.853 --> 50:07.273
Let's pray.

50:08.916 --> 50:10.258
Our Father, thank You,

50:10.530 --> 50:15.097
Thank you that your love for us is an initiative taking love.

50:16.339 --> 50:18.863
Otherwise, by nature, we don't seek you.

50:19.344 --> 50:22.929
By nature, we try to fix everything ourselves.

50:23.871 --> 50:28.839
And it is a wonder when we realize that we're broken and that we need you, Jesus.

50:29.740 --> 50:32.865
So we pray that you will meet us where we are because you know us.

50:33.586 --> 50:36.050
And it is for your voice that we want to listen.

50:36.674 --> 50:53.853
And it is your hand that we want to reach out and take hold of us so that whatever this day remains for us to bring, that we might say, I heard the voice of Jesus and I came to Him.

50:54.854 --> 51:04.385
Here are prayers and enable us to look to you unreservedly as we pray in Jesus' name.

51:05.146 --> 51:05.586
Amen.

